          Empezar prueba gratuita
          <svg class="ml-1.5 inline-block size-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" /></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:info@inventowry.com" class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-300 px-7 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-zinc-700 transition-all hover:bg-white hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5">
          Hablar con ventas
